    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s smooth, shiny, and ready for all your adventures. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to believe how clean it is! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
