      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 993-generation Carrera is a superlative example of air-cooled engineering, featuring the 3.6L M64 flat-six mated to a G50 6-speed manual transaxle with a factory limited-slip differential. The powertrain is mechanically tight, showing no evidence of oil seepage from the valve covers or chain housings. The chassis utilizes the refined multi-link LSA rear suspension, providing exceptional kinematic toe control and lateral stability. All bushings remain compliant, and the Bilstein dampers offer factory-spec rebound and compression. The Bosch Motronic fuel injection system ensures a steady idle and linear power delivery across the rev range. This vehicle presents in concours-level condition, with pristine paint depth and an interior free of UV degradation or bolster wear. A mechanically sound, turnkey specimen for the air-cooled purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Clean title. Full service history included. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
