    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that defines the term 'mint.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring the factory paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks or rock chips. The exterior has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assists, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the buyer who demands perfection and refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
