    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled distinction, maintained to the most exacting standards. This specimen exhibits a pristine exterior finish and an interior that remains in showroom condition, devoid of any discernible wear. Mechanically, it operates with the precision of a new assembly, having undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure it meets our premier tier of excellence. For the discerning driver who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
