    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive example of JDM engineering. This A80 retains its factory-spec 2JZ-GTE 3.0L twin-turbocharged inline-six, mated to the coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. The sequential turbocharger system operates with surgical precision, providing a linear power band and robust boost pressure. Mechanically, the vehicle is impeccable: the Torsen limited-slip differential, four-wheel double-wishbone suspension, and four-piston ventilated disc brakes are all in optimal condition. The engine bay is a testament to preservation, featuring original heat shielding, factory vacuum lines, and all matching VIN tags. This unmodified specimen delivers the exact steering feedback and longitudinal stability intended by Toyota's performance division, making it a rare acquisition for the discerning collector.",
